The paper proposes a method for video object segmentation using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The method involves learning embeddings and appearance models, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of parallel convolutional operations, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) research.
